A man has been sentenced to 15 years in jail for defiling a minor. Walter Nyangau Ombati was found guilty of defiling the girl, 16, on May 4, 2017 at Majengo estate in the outskirts of Narok town. ALSO READ:

My gamble with grapes drips of sweet success The court heard the accused lured the minor to his house and defiled her. “I find that the girl's testimony recounting the incidences of the night she was defiled as graphic and  truthful,” ruled Narok Senior Resident Magistrate Hosea Ng’ang’a.